
Where to start
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
See the "doc" directory, where you will find
a "quickstart" guide for the FMS AM3 model.


Summary of directory contents
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
bin/
     -- mkmf script for creating Makefiles
     -- template files for the mkmf script
     -- list_paths generates a list of source files using find
     -- time_stamp.csh used by run script

doc/ 
     -- quickstart guide

exp/
     -- model input files for the AM3 experiment, such as:
           namelists, diagnostics tables, field tables.
     -- compile script. (uses mkmf)
     -- list of source code. (used by mkmf)
     -- run script for running the model.

postprocessing/
     -- source code for processing model output.

src/   
     -- source code for the AM3 model

tools/
    -- source code for interpolation of model output
       to a lat-lon grid.
